    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a factory-spec limited-slip differential and recent suspension bushing refreshes. Crucially, the VANOS system has been serviced and the rear subframe inspected for structural integrity, ensuring this high-revving power unit is ready for the redline. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp. A driver-spec machine optimized for corner-exit traction and engagement.",
