    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer looking for a reliable, well-maintained luxury sedan. Finished in a classic Deep Metallic Grey, the exterior retains a brilliant shine with only minor road-pebble chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. The interior is a smoke-free environment featuring supple charcoal leather; the seats show minimal bolster wear and the walnut wood trim remains crack-free. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. I have kept a meticulous folder of service records, including a recent oil change, brake pad replacement, and a fresh set of all-season tires with 80% tread remaining. Every electronic feature\u2014from the heated seats to the premium sound system and navigation\u2014functions exactly as it should. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the engine runs quiet and strong with no leaks or warning lights. While there is a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door, the overall presentation is sharp and impressive. It is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
